Coins.ph is on a mission to create an open financial system by providing everyone easy access to Web3 and digital assets. A regulated entity, Coins is the most established crypto brand in the Philippines and has gained the trust of more than 16 million users. Through the easy-to-use mobile app, users can buy and sell a variety of different cryptocurrencies and also access a wide range of payment services.
What you will do
Integrate various logs sources with SIEM / Data Platform;
Automate the detection and response tasks;
SIEM / Data Platform content improvement;
Communicate with all levels of technology and operational staff, assist in the creation and follow methodologies, creating clear, concise deliverables.
Qualification and Skills
3-5 years of experience in an Information Security role;
Scripting in Python, Bash, or any other scripting languages;
SQL knowledge;
Experience with automating incident detection and response;
Intermediate knowledge of the English language.
